originalText.text: I'm so glad I was able to experience a Disney audition coaching with Emma! I immediately felt comfortable with her as she was super welcoming, positive and friendly throughout the entire session. I feel so much more confident and prepared to go into my audition after having this session with her. She was well prepared, and tailored the session to what I wanted to work on personally. What I loved most about Emma was that she didn't make me feel like just another one of her clients. Rather, I truly felt the genuine care that she had for me and my success as a performer, as I'm positive she does with all her other clients as well. She had amazing constructive criticism and lots of useful tips and tricks to share. She even stayed to chat with me a bit longer than scheduled and has made herself available to stay in contact with any questions that I may have even after the audition coaching is over. I would highly recommend booking a session with her, you won't regret it!

originalText.text:
Coaching with Emma is a must for anyone auditioning for Disney.

1. She let me know everything I could expect at the various types of calls, and patiently answered my (many) questions ;)

2. She tailored her coaching to what I, as a performer, was not yet confident about. Her guidance, especially with Animations, was very specific and incredibly helpful.

3. Her positive feedback made me feel really confident and self-assured, which I carried with me into each audition.

I believe Emma's coaching is a big, big reason I did so well, stood out to the CDs, and got so far at the open calls I have attended so far. She is a pro, a Disney expert, and a resource of knowledge on this that I don't think exists anywhere else. Well worth it.

originalText.text: We hired Emma as a singing telegram for one of our coworker’s birthdays. Emma went above and beyond to understand our asks and included amazing personal touches into the custom song. We loved the costume and the balloon she brought, but the most impactful part was the energy she brought to the performance. 10/10 would recommend!
